model_overview:
The dataset has the following attributes: CAR car acceptability, PRICE overall price, buying buying price, maint price of 
    the maintenance, TECH technical characteristics, COMFORT comfort, doors number of doors, persons capacity in terms of persons to carry, 
    lug_boot the size of luggage boot, safety estimated safety of the car Input attributes are printed in lowercase

model_ethical_consideration_risks.name:
The Car Evaluation Database contains examples with the structural information removed, i.e., 
                     directly relates CAR to the six input attributes: buying, maint, doors, persons, lug_boot, safety.
model_ethical_consideration_risks.mitigation_strategy: Ensure that the dataset is representative of the real world data.

model_ethical_limitations.description: This database may be particularly useful for testing constructive induction and structure discovery methods
